    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――脚本のサンプルが届いてすぐ",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日はレッスンルームで、瑠依がサキュバス役の）\n（練習をしているんだったな……様子を見てみるか）",
      "startTime": 5.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "「わ、私のも、ものに……\nし、してあげてもいい、わ、よ」",
      "startTime": 13.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……全然ダメだわ。『誘惑するように』って……\n一体どうすればいいのよ……",
      "startTime": 23.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3233.333333400001,
          "startTime": 26.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "こっちのセリフは……「そ、そんなことも\n出来ないなんて、私が、いないとダメなの、ね……？」",
      "startTime": 30.5625870377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "「さぁ、ひ、ひざまじゅっ……ひざまずいてっ！\nわ、私のく、く、靴……靴を舐め、なさい……」",
      "startTime": 41.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（……どうしたんだ？　やけにぎこちないな）\n（演技は苦手じゃなかったはずだけど……）",
      "startTime": 51.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！　{user}さん！？\nい、いつからそこに……！？",
      "startTime": 56.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "うっ、そんな目で見ないで下さい\n……自分でも全然ダメだって分かっています",
      "startTime": 62.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "役作りに難航しているようだな……\n瑠依はまだサキュバスに抵抗があるのか？",
      "startTime": 69.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、もう気持ちは固まっています。むしろ今は\nしっかり役作りに取り組みたいんです、けど……",
      "startTime": 76.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "真面目にやろうとすればするほど、恥ずかしくなって\n……自分でも迷走している自覚は、あります",
      "startTime": 84.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……。でも、やる気はこの間より\nさらに増しているみたいだな。何かあったのか？",
      "startTime": 92.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "実は、配役が決まってから\n同じサキュバス役の千紗と、話をしたんですけど",
      "startTime": 99.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "「ちょっと恥ずかしいけど、応援してきてくれた\n人達へのお返しになるなら頑張る」と言っていて",
      "startTime": 106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "その時、痛感したんです。私は千紗ほど覚悟が決まって\nいなかった。ファンへの気持ちも中途半端だったって",
      "startTime": 114.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "サキュバスで、その……エ、エッチなのは\nやっぱりまだ、恥ずかしいですけど……",
      "startTime": 124.3666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくファンと一緒に作るゲームなんですから\n私も、少しでもファンにお返しがしたいと思ったんです",
      "startTime": 130.6721720286,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4242.274230000021,
          "startTime": 134.9144462586
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "でも……この『上から目線で小馬鹿にするように』とか\n『惑わすように』っていう演技が分からなくて……",
      "startTime": 139.5333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "強引に迫るシーンも多いですし……\n生意気で偉そうで、傲慢なだけに思えてしまって",
      "startTime": 145.9075392527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私が演じるキャラクターの見た目なんですけど\n肌の露出が多くて、自分だと思うと恥ずかしくて……",
      "startTime": 154.627089873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。まだキャラを掴めていないってことか\n俺は瑠依にピッタリだと思ったんだけど……",
      "startTime": 164.8212859333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "どこがピッタリなんですか！？　……え？\nまさか私、生意気で偉そうで傲慢なんですか……？",
      "startTime": 172.0666753133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それはどちらかというとkanaさんとか……ゴホン\nいや、瑠依がそういう性格だって話じゃないよ",
      "startTime": 182.7333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんに聞かれたら大変なことになりそうですが\n……では、どういう意味ですか？",
      "startTime": 190.7000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、そうだな……うまく言えないけど、まずは\n演じるキャラクターへの理解を深めてみたらどうだ？",
      "startTime": 198.4094403386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "今の瑠依は、「サキュバスというのはこういうものだ」\nっていうイメージに、囚われ過ぎているように見える",
      "startTime": 205.1666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "……言われてみれば私、イメージだけで知った気に\nなっていて、深くは知らないかもしれません",
      "startTime": 211.6723912321,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7432.791274199985,
          "startTime": 219.1051825063
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、{user}さん\n私……ちょっと、行ってきます！",
      "startTime": 217.9333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "おーい、瑠依……どこに行くつもりだ？\n……大丈夫かな",
      "startTime": 226.3666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 228.9118904871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、今日この後って\n私、オフですよね？",
      "startTime": 233.9333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "実は、優にサキュバスが出てくる漫画やゲームを\nいくつか教えてもらったんです",
      "startTime": 239.6333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui023.m4a",
      "text": "この後、その作品を探しに、書店やゲームショップに\n行ってみようかと思って",
      "startTime": 245.566666158,
